body_html: The repr also looks off for one of the tensors: they both print the same but are of different dtypes. Presumably this is because one is float and one is long and you can usually differentiate which is which based on the values, but there are no values here. So probably need to special case this (I believe empty is interpreted as floating point if no dtype is present).
